Seller has done a LOT of cosmetic work to the home - it still could use some Personal Touches here and there, but the home has Magnificent Potential!! Home is BOASTFUL; New(er) Vinyl Windows, Metal Roof, Heating Elements, Updated interior Paint, Exterior fully Painted, Etc.! HUGE Attic - Could be Master Suite, Bonus Space, or Storage! Privacy Fenced Yard, Enclosed Side Porch, Rear Deck, and Balcony - Lots of Placed to Render a Peaceful Retreat!! Side Porch is 16x9; Could be Enclosed Garden, Hobby Nook, Coffee Nook, or just a Cute Hang-out Area! Rear Deck is 10x17; BBQ Away!! Detail is not spared in this home; (2) Living Rooms, “Butlers Staircase” off kitchen, Arched Hallway, Large Laundry Room on Bedroom Level!!  Spacious Rooms w/ High Ceilings!
